Package gov.cdc.izgw.v2tofhir.annotation

Annotation Interface ComesFrom

@Repeatable(List.class) @Target({TYPE,METHOD}) @Retention(RUNTIME) @Documented public @interface ComesFrom
This annotation is used to document V2 to FHIR segment conversions. In the future, it may be used to automate such conversions.
Author:
Audacious Inquiry
